{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u68f1378f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">除了提供丰富的文字编辑能力，语雀还提供了种类丰富的特色卡片，让文档拥有丰富的应用能力，如投票、打卡、日历等。</span></p><p id=\"u94283254\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1654588469142-d1e773da-6bca-4221-81c8-e012ac3f1b29.png\" width=\"750\" id=\"u20afe074\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"ujOaH\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如何插入特色卡片</span></h2><p id=\"u4382922f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">目前有两种方式支持插入语雀的特色卡片</span></p><p id=\"u67e3488e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1.通过顶部编辑栏左侧的</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649645948281-8c650900-92c0-448d-a049-5012238dab2d.png\" width=\"17\" id=\"vDSal\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">按钮插入特色卡片    2.通过 斜杠命令 /插入特色卡片<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649658807000-d01e3b25-6068-48bc-8bc9-d3ea553f66ee.png\" width=\"107\" id=\"gWIvY\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649658807000-d01e3b25-6068-48bc-8bc9-d3ea553f66ee.png\" width=\"98\" id=\"dB7zP\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649662155792-b7191f70-94c0-441b-b970-7eab59208ffb.png\" width=\"501\" id=\"u16a47215\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ufc0100b2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"hWpGK\"><span class=\"ne-text\">有哪些特色卡片？</span></h2><p id=\"u79cffe1d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当前语雀有很多类有意思的小卡片。当你想插入试试时，尝试输入斜杠 / 和对应卡片的拼音缩写。</span></p><p id=\"u2763dbeb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h3 id=\"blrDT\"><span class=\"ne-text\">使用画板画个图</span></h3><p id=\"u52d75b7d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过插入画板卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/hb</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可以快速插入一个画板卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u1f0dcd9a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">自由画板支持包括思维导图、流程图、UML和架构图等多种类型，形状和连线的自由成组排列，自由画图。</span></p><p id=\"uce3790b6\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649669429519-c44cad8d-05f6-45b4-b0a6-4bb15ed4666e.png\" width=\"764\" id=\"FVPxb\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/268442/1649669699058-a3e2c365-d66c-4580-a60b-1fa5daf9ff0f.jpeg\" id=\"CT0af\" style=\"display: block; width: 100%\"><p id=\"u7a8d15c8\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"YX3hb\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/editor-mind-map\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/editor-mind-map</a></span></p><p id=\"u22e4e447\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"jxxBy\"><span class=\"ne-text\">使用表格记录汇总</span></h3><p id=\"u448c0a74\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过插入表格卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/bg</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可以快速插入一个表格卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u9a2561fa\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649669860618-9c814a28-64f0-4ecf-ac2f-a0260ed5f0ab.png\" width=\"764\" id=\"Fomd7\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><table id=\"slVSR\" class=\"ne-table no-border\" style=\"width: 741px\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"741\" colspan=\"8\" style=\"background-color: #FAFAFA\"><p id=\"u69c8fada\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">一周安排</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"86\"></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\"><p id=\"u5ee44b5b\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周一</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\"><p id=\"uc9e33823\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周二</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\"><p id=\"u10763193\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周三</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\"><p id=\"ue9746e53\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周四</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\"><p id=\"ub8b9805d\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周五</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"93\" style=\"background-color: #E9E9E9\"><p id=\"ucc352ca7\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周六</span></strong></p></td><td width=\"97\" style=\"background-color: #E9E9E9\"><p id=\"uc49b6685\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">周日</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"86\" style=\"background-color: #FAFAFA\"><p id=\"u7c4484bc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">上午</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u95b7ea23\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">计划</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"ud32d83c9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">项目复盘</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"ud2996d89\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u2a000b63\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u66b37bc2\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><ul class=\"ne-tl\"><li id=\"uc2ae82b8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🥏飞盘</span></li></ul></td><td width=\"97\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"86\" style=\"background-color: #FAFAFA\"><p id=\"uc2e060e0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">下午</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"ub76bc21f\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u221f6285\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u45ccc0a1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">周会</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"ued8b4049\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p></td><td width=\"93\"><ul class=\"ne-tl\"><li id=\"u8c71b1bb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></li></ul></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"97\"><ul class=\"ne-tl\"><li id=\"u88c382f5\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🏊游泳</span></li></ul></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"86\" style=\"background-color: #FAFAFA\"><p id=\"u8be83cd0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">晚上</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><ul class=\"ne-tl\"><li checked=\"true\" id=\"uf75f1883\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🧘‍♀️瑜伽</span></li></ul></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"93\"></td><td width=\"97\"></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"86\" style=\"background-color: #FAFAFA\"><p id=\"u5d406bdd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">心情指数</span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u6acdb918\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA\">         </span><span class=\"ne-text\">           </span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u824ca411\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #D4EEFC\">                </span><span class=\"ne-text\">    </span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"ubae9d569\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA\">         </span><span class=\"ne-text\">           </span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u7d8d8c8e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA\">         </span><span class=\"ne-text\">           </span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u00f860cc\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA\">            </span><span class=\"ne-text\">        </span></p></td><td width=\"93\"><p id=\"u85db94ba\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #E4F7D2\">                 </span><span class=\"ne-text\">   </span></p></td><td width=\"97\"><p id=\"u776e66d2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FFE8E6\">          </span><span class=\"ne-text\">          </span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p id=\"ub7d6cea0\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"udbe691fe\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"x9mXd\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/wbsu70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/wbsu70</a></span></p><p id=\"ud94437a3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"C7oc4\"><span class=\"ne-text\">构建知识网络</span></h3><p id=\"u3c3ac415\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀还提供知识网络的能力，让文档可以跨越组织地关联到一起，形成一张知识网络。</span></p><h4 id=\"RaOYY\"><span class=\"ne-text\">粘贴语雀链接</span></h4><p id=\"ucae5e6f4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在文档中，通过直接粘贴链接的方式，构建知识关联。</span></p><p id=\"u7013c7e3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持四种形式的链接：原链接、标题形态、卡片形态、嵌入形态。</span></p><table id=\"AlQCY\" class=\"ne-table no-border\" style=\"width: 677px\"><tbody><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"ucd636b6b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">链接形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><p id=\"u0ece3941\" class=\"ne-p\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</span></a></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"u9f8e29c1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">标题形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><p id=\"u6654d70d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span id=\"TzfcC\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"u8265aa34\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">卡片形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><div id=\"FaKIv\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></div></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 33px\"><td width=\"87\"><p id=\"ua0d13ff2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">嵌入形态</span></p></td><td width=\"590\"><div id=\"nsBXi\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/explore/headlines</a></div></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id=\"mdkgh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过 @ 提及</span></h4><p id=\"u1bf58415\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文中输入 </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #F5F5F5\">@</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #BFBFBF; background-color: #F5F5F5\">提及</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> ，可提及语雀内容和人。可搜索到你访问的语雀内容范围。本知识库、本团队优先显示。</span></p><p id=\"u014c83db\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655193995304-4f295c67-a2b0-4198-a59f-da1ed782d3b9.png\" width=\"363\" id=\"rRrvE\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187544348-62072849-a6ec-46b5-844c-0971e7234a16.png\" width=\"366\" id=\"Dq53K\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h4 id=\"g3LxT\"><span class=\"ne-text\">引入语雀内容</span></h4><p id=\"u3e0aca7e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过左上角加号面板</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655186849939-164bcd8f-aa6b-4654-83c0-5370d0fe7e27.png\" width=\"15\" id=\"u59bd08bc\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">，或斜杠输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/语雀内容</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可快速搜索插入内容。</span></p><p id=\"u388b1122\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187070047-f3b41c1e-f935-493c-8920-19ec85ba56ef.png\" width=\"302\" id=\"u626dce1a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u5f68a757\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655187284966-53878a89-731b-4305-a76f-fbc6184088aa.png\" width=\"774\" id=\"ud13ca39d\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ua79ec877\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">具体详见 </span><span id=\"kx3KN\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/gh3mdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/gh3mdb</a></span><span class=\"ne-text\"> </span><span id=\"AntBH\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/aint7x\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/aint7x</a></span></p><p id=\"u1b1e722c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"gI29U\"><span class=\"ne-text\">嵌入本地文件和附件</span></h3><p id=\"u69af205a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过上传本地文件 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/wj</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">和附件</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fj</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，唤起本地文件夹目录，选择你想上传展示的文件类型。目前支持 PDF、Office系列、Sketch文件、音视频文件格式等。（视频文件需成为会员方可上传）</span></p><p id=\"udfb91dfa\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655109855706-d718d2cf-019e-470d-bfad-d4beb2b2f0c1.png\" width=\"164\" id=\"wSZq5\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649735016226-d6b40f16-5701-4b57-bf7d-f0096047d139.png\" width=\"558\" id=\"lzuG6\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uecec4a44\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u8401fc11\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持从本地文件夹窗口直接拖拽文件，嵌入语雀文档内。可在弹窗和工具栏中选择展示的形态。</span></p><p id=\"ued45ec6a\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655110046614-5cebadcd-f056-4d25-bcb1-aafe5c528503.png\" width=\"210\" id=\"nudV6\" class=\"ne-image\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655110438708-5bc8e8b0-64a2-4581-8300-29f8ea7cea0b.png\" width=\"526\" id=\"d4zDw\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u5e02afc8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ucc5116a5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可设置在阅读端是否可被下载。</span></p><p id=\"u4cb9bd6d\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655110136652-d5dc8121-e65b-4112-b56d-ff70089c505e.png\" width=\"393\" id=\"NgjvR\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u3a10f30b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u34a6e214\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"aSTY3\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/uilmir\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/uilmir</a></span></p><h3 id=\"zI0Uf\"><span class=\"ne-text\">发起投票活动</span></h3><p id=\"u0b75b39b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过插入投票卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/vote</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可以快速设置和发起一个投票活动。</span></p><p id=\"ub251982c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置好标题、选项和截止时间后，阅读端即可点击投票，实时显示已投票的统计。</span></p><p id=\"ub314f707\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u9615fc68\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649666917543-4f912945-43a5-441c-be5e-d3ab54aadb3a.png\" width=\"764\" id=\"ub520901f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ua4066ca1\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649666836043-6ae55209-7ae2-48a6-8653-f6a0850e655a.png\" width=\"744\" id=\"u3c533ecc\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><div id=\"Nyl6A\" class=\"ne-vote\">此处为语雀投票卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#Nyl6A\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#Nyl6A</a></div><p id=\"u8cfc4000\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"fBhC8\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/idbcog\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/idbcog</a></span></p><p id=\"uab94b002\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"RZHpa\"><span class=\"ne-text\">发起打卡活动</span></h3><p id=\"u584f7caa\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过插入打卡卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/dk</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可以快速设置和发起一个打卡活动。</span></p><p id=\"ua6130f23\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">hover在卡片上，出现编辑按钮。或直接点击卡片，可修改打卡文案。</span></p><p id=\"u9d8c2a15\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">设置好标题、按钮文案和截止时间后，阅读端即可点击打卡，实时显示已打卡的统计。</span></p><p id=\"u3cac1a5d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ue9d44959\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649668017770-e4fe7b9b-2e40-4262-944d-a3bdc6a8114f.png\" width=\"766\" id=\"ub4ab7a2e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u6f46e70c\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649668164310-67faa3a5-dd26-428e-9710-bc6a50481589.png\" width=\"768\" id=\"ud6a3253a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><div id=\"zcgam\" class=\"ne-check-in\">此处为语雀打卡卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#zcgam\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#zcgam</a></div><p id=\"u7d843f37\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"YNX6U\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/txaf3z\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/txaf3z</a></span></p><p id=\"u0dee367b\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"DhunY\"><span class=\"ne-text\">使用日历添加日程</span></h3><p id=\"u942e7f4d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过插入日历卡片</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/rl</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，可以快速插入一个日历卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u5d1b4a9e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在月视图下可自由新建和拖拽调整日程，方便你的旅行策划或日程管理。</span></p><p id=\"u3209f377\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649668646500-8714e258-cb0f-4661-a017-c5443c692614.png\" width=\"765\" id=\"TQ2Vp\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc6886ddb\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1649668843937-7f8b9887-e00a-4417-b234-ddb2685fb006.png\" width=\"726\" id=\"Ej4HQ\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><div id=\"nTQEJ\" class=\"ne-calendar\">此处为语雀日历卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#nTQEJ\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/fq1pad#nTQEJ</a></div><p id=\"ud48511b4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"jBPY3\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/oghrhg\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/oghrhg</a></span></p><p id=\"ucb76d72c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"Nof2D\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用高亮块缤纷你的内容</span></h3><p id=\"u2fc456e1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文区域输入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/glk</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/高亮</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，选择高亮块卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u18ecf865\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655112021471-1359c140-857c-455f-b770-18ff4c0f121e.png\" width=\"288\" id=\"ubff72d93\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u94c1ba65\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">:::</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">之后按下回车键</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Enter</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，即可创建高亮块。</span></p><div data-type=\"color1\" class=\"ne-alert\"><p id=\"u0bcb011f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p></div><p id=\"ucfdff2b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"uf690d040\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在高亮块内，支持多段落的富文本格式，支持内嵌链接、标题等格式。支持内嵌图片、附件、嵌入文件等卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u15ad1108\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h1 id=\"hyZRD\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀，构建你的数字花园</span></h1><p id=\"u3d3d479e\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655108167870-8f045866-6e1b-4c6a-8213-4f8f29eb093b.png\" width=\"517\" id=\"hANtm\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"udb9797a0\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/download\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/download\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">下载客户端</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">\t\t</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/dashboard\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/dashboard\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">体验网页版</span></a></p><p id=\"u02aebdee\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u58a6c478\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更多问题移步 → </span><span id=\"UQ44f\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\" style=\"font-size: 13px\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/topics\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/topics</a></span></p><p id=\"ua1764c0b\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br></p></div><p id=\"u35bf264c\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u58e6625b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">高亮块也支持被嵌入到其他卡片中，如折叠卡片、分栏卡片和表格中。</span></p><details class=\"lake-collapse\"><summary id=\"uc051eded\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠卡片，内容可以收起不看</span></summary></details><p id=\"u86b32e3d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"WqbSy\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/rhhxkx\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/rhhxkx</a></span></p><h3 id=\"sh4j6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用折叠块让陈述有详有略</span></h3><p id=\"u2c9aacdf\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文区域输入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/zd</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/折叠</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，选择折叠块。</span></p><p id=\"u875bfc75\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655114759322-904fde79-923e-42a9-b050-5349a337895c.png\" width=\"279\" id=\"fukPO\" class=\"ne-image\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38)\"></p><p id=\"u055fc9b3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">折叠块内支持嵌入多种内容。包括富文本段落、引用、分割线、高亮块、图片、附件、链接、标题、卡片等。</span></p><details class=\"lake-collapse\"><summary id=\"u5cde1f4e\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38)\">像书一样的知识库</span></summary><div class=\"ne-quote\"><p id=\"u7318306a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90)\">语雀特色的目录及大纲功能，让多篇文档结构化，形成一本本像书一样清晰易读的知识库，方便知识 创作及沉淀。</span></p></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"HXP7V\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38)\">目录编排\t</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/thyzgp/vlki63\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/thyzgp/vlki63\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">了解更多</span></a></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u650d32c6\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">简单、强大的目录编辑，让你的知识库文档结构可以和书本一样清晰易读</span></li></ul></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"ye0JA\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-size: 19px\">互动交流</span></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u351a6e39\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">创作之外，让所有成员可以在同一个地方进行互动交流，让想法碰撞更有趣，沟通更充分。</span></li></ul></div><div data-type=\"tips\" class=\"ne-alert\"><h4 id=\"FVUoL\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-size: 19px\">权限管理\t</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/qa/kybteg\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/qa/kybteg\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">了解更多</span></a></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6aa725ce\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(88, 90, 90); background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250)\">可以对知识库人员进行精细化管理，按需调整只读、编辑复制、分享，下载等相关权限，安全尽在掌握</span></li></ul></div><p id=\"u3693fbe0\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655128326157-c97f0dd0-068e-4cd9-a0c5-18e576063148.png\" width=\"427\" id=\"u8281a2a3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><div id=\"o233y\" class=\"ne-yuque\">此处为语雀内容卡片，点击链接查看：<a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/changelog/roadmap#sAFb4AQIyGg9hMH2pYnM6fX71dnqIkXo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/changelog/roadmap#sAFb4AQIyGg9hMH2pYnM6fX71dnqIkXo</a></div></details><p id=\"u54eb46ae\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑端点击发布后，编辑端设置的折叠块收起/展开的样式，会成为阅读端默认的样式。<br /></span><span class=\"ne-text\">阅读者可以点击展开收起。</span></p><p id=\"u7bd3b3bb\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见 </span><span id=\"bv0ba\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/ep53bo\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/ep53bo</a></span></p><h3 id=\"rFZGk\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用分栏卡片实现多列布局</span></h3><p id=\"u93ae193b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">分栏卡片是一种块级卡片，提供一行多栏的布局。让文档的排版能力更加丰富。</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1655435994606-9b5e194a-c805-4bfb-9fc0-78de375ae5fd.png\" width=\"275\" id=\"ubeebc18f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ua5697a33\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u985fca41\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在正文区域输入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fl2</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fl3</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fl4</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，创建分栏布局。</span></p><p id=\"u947a11e2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1655446463754-dcb8cedb-cb23-4b2b-8036-2879de2be71d.gif\" width=\"1964\" id=\"udfc452e9\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ub0d27d8d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见</span><span id=\"V44xJ\" class=\"ne-yuque-inline\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/eb14rq\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/eb14rq</a></span></p><h3 id=\"nuQiY\"><span class=\"ne-text\">还有更多…</span></h3><p id=\"ud2a0ee7b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://yuque.antfin.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://yuque.antfin.com/feedbacks/new\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">  感谢你的支持！</span></p><p id=\"u7acc02b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u11b03917\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u5626432e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u1efaaf68\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ub967a760\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"u096d0d3b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p></div>",
